title: Fwithargou-2 Jisua fwithargou
lyrics:
Fwithargou-2 Jisua fwithargou
Thamtim ja-2 Jisujwng thangfanw -2
Gaojwng gaobw onjlaidw
Dai fwrkhoubw khema hwdw -2
(De khema hwdw de)
(A)
Gwrbw khamgli nanwi
Bika souwi-souwi
Fwidw fwi Iswrnao -2
(De fwifinthardw de)
(B)
Wi subung harifwr
Phapjwng gelenaifwr
Fwidw de fwi Iswrnao -2
(De fwifinthardw de)
